{
  "stem": "24259.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And things used to go through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the cows, of course, would urinate and whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it would go through, so the hole was very damp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only thing that we had to line the hole was straw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what little clothes we had was very minimal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were just like rags, and certainly, our feet and most of our body was bare.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there were no blankets or-- most of the things that we had were like rags and from potato sacks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they [? would. ?] Whatever we had available, they would just wrap our feet and-- and body with sacks and so forth.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were-- the clothes were just tattered and worn out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, they would get wet and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So was not very comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was very cold most of the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, again, I remember the dampness and so forth, and the darkness.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I personally remember that, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember too many of the other specifics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Occasionally, my father would go out during the night and see if he could find some extra food for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the people and the farmers were, themselves, quite poor, and they had just about enough food to feed themselves.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as kind as they would try to be to give us a little bit, I mean, good food would be a potato or a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that would be the-- the-- the good food to have.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But occasionally, my father would go out and-- and pick berries or-- or fruit when it was available.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He would literally steal it from other farmers and so forth, in the woods, and-- and bring it back so we'd-- we'd stay alive.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
